    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Plants with prostrate or low spreading growth that cover the surface of the earth and that smother weeds. Generally used in landscaping in place of turf.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
